{"tid":1588831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"澄清仇警言論並刪除社交帳號　見習律師獲執業許可","createTime":"2019-09-23T04:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T04:07:27.000Z","uid":241239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd26924f1d1fe82cf87a94f2ad84a80e219a01ee","tid":1588831,"uid":241239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"早前在網上發布粗言穢語及仇警言論的一名見習律師，早上在高等法院宣誓，正式獲得執業許可。<br />\n<br />\n律政司代表律師在庭上表示，相信有關仇警言論是他的女友借用其Facebook戶口發表，女友亦撰信致歉，而該名見習律師過往亦未曾發佈有關言論，認為他有良好的性格，事後他亦已立即刪除帳號，因此不會就其執業申請提出反對。<br />\n<br />\n法官陸啟康批准其律師執業認許，但他表示，事件演變成涉及公眾利益並引起傳媒關注，認為有關言論不單傷害警察自身，同時亦傷害他們無辜的家人，又勸勉他即將成為律師，應小心謹慎言論，相信他會得到教訓，明白自己衝動地行使言論自由時亦需要付出代價。<br />\n<br />\n見習律師朱承曄早前因在網上發布粗言穢語及仇警言論，遭人投訴行為不當並要求律政司拒絕其律師動議申請。律政司早前亦已表示，經考慮後已接納當事人的解釋，並已通知當事人，律政司不會就其執業申請提出反對。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c04f879f2e85b167b07db022c14caa2c9ab3238","tid":1588831,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"b9769cada713991a8d8e24f87bbb63736da2637e","tid":1588831,"uid":241239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482053-20190923.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482053-20190923.htm&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=61aeb9f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482053-20190923.htm&h=2fb6d518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482053-20190923.htm</a>"},{"pid":"aa11aaa08b87d89e0f57f56dd60265c09927a155","tid":1588831,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"唔怪得佢"}]}